2020 is in the books, and what a uniquely bleak year it was. From film delays to deaths, quarantines and riots it was a year like no other. Join the guys at Comic Book Clique as they sift through the year that was 2020 and look for a some nuggets of good within the bad. With all of the feature films, televisions shows, comics and news to come out of 2020, will the good outweigh the bad? Or was 2020 more fortuitous then we gave it credit for? Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! Please [SUPPORT US ON PATREON](http://Patreon.com/CBCClubhouse)!

